-- BHP Takeover of Potash Would Be `Major Loss' for Canada, Jarislowsky Says
-- B y   D a v i d   S c a n l a n
-- 2010-11-02T19:11:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/bhp-takeover-of-potash-would-be-major-loss-for-canada-jarislowsky-says.html
BHP Billiton Ltd’s takeover of Potash
Corp. of Saskatchewan Inc. would represent a “major loss” and
a “mistake” for Canada, said Stephen Jarislowsky, chief
executive officer of Jarislowsky Fraser Ltd., a money manager
and Potash shareholder based in Montreal. Jarislowsky spoke in
an interview today on BNN Television.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  